&lt;li&gt;Partner closely with Lyft’s Corporate Development team and Treasury team as well as advise company leadership and cross-functional stakeholders (e.g. people, accounting, tax, treasury, operations, etc.) on novel corporate legal issues and risks of corporate transactions.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Responsible for drafting and negotiating NDAs, LOIs/term sheets and definitive transaction agreements as well as driving diligence processes.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Shape and improve our legal processes that enable both legal and business functions to scale effectively.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Assist other teams with projects on an as-needed basis.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
