&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;4+ years of experience practicing corporate and securities law, with an emphasis on M&amp;amp;A and strategic transactions; experience at a top-tier law firm required; in-house experience at a public company is a strong plus.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Degree from top-tier law school.&lt;/li&gt;
