&lt;li&gt;3-5 years of experience with a mix of business analytics in a high growth or complex business, investment banking with strong analytical exposure and/or role at a top-tier consulting firm&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Deep understanding of complex data models, BI methodologies, data architecture principles and metadata&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proficient in SQL and working with raw data sets. (Python or other programming languages is a huge plus.)&lt;/li&gt;
