&lt;li&gt;Forecast operational requirements needed to maintain high service levels and meet contractual and financial targets&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Work with our bike &amp;amp; scooter share markets to deliver ongoing support and deep dive analyses on performance; monitor and diagnose performance and present findings to key stakeholders&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate with cross-functional teammates to tackle complex problems including: asset maintenance, system health and labor forecasting&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
